description: Jake Steel is preparing Mason Wyler something special for just being himself. Jake is a great baker and he wants to excite Mason as much as possible.Mason is surprised to see Jake walk in with some yummy brownie batter. They both taste the goods and exchange it with some chocolate swapping.Sticky treats are great and Jake has more instore for Mason. These two hunks share every hole with a passionate intent. Big cocks,lots of slobbering and great butts to give any man a raging hard on.Enjoy!
title: Baked Goods
